docs {
  # List All Users
  
  Retrieves a list of all users in the system.
  
  ## Request
  - **Method**: GET
  - **Endpoint**: `/api/v1/users`
  
  ## Response (200 OK)
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "John Doe",
        "email": "john@example.com"
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "name": "Jane Smith",
        "email": "jane@example.com"
      }
    ]
  }
  ```
  
  ## Error Responses
  - **500 Internal Server Error**: Database or server error
}
